Package Description
com.wizzer.mle.math
This package contains math utilities for the Magic Lantern SDK.

Magic Lantern SDK - Math Library

The Magic Lantern Software Development Kit provides a library of math utilities to facilitate title development. The math library contains classes for vectors with 2, 3 and 4 floating-point elements. The library also provides a 4x3 affine matrix of floating-point elements.
